<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Craven1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Craven,</orth> subst. coward: <bibl n="shak. h5 4.7.139" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 7, 139</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.1.15" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 1, 15</bibl>. Used of a beaten cock: <cit><quote>no cock of mine, you crow too like a c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 2.228" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. II, 228</bibl></cit>.
